description: [``botocore``] This release updates the CreateAssessmentFrameworkControlSet and UpdateAssessmentFrameworkControlSet API data types. For both of these data types, the control set name is now a required attribute.
[``botocore``] Documentation Updates for Amazon Nimble Studio.
[``botocore``] Amazon Kinesis Analytics now supports RollbackApplication for Apache Flink applications to revert the application to the previous running version
[``botocore``] Amazon SageMaker Autopilot now provides the ability to automatically deploy the best model to an endpoint
